## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="af626-129">L'esempio seguente crea una grammatica per un'applicazione che restituisce informazioni su service bus shuttle.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af626-129">The following example creates a grammar for an application that returns information about bus shuttle service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af626-130">Il primo metodo, `GrammarUrlForRoute`, accetta una stringa che specifica una route e lo aggiunge alla stringa che specifica il percorso di una grammatica.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af626-130">The first method, `GrammarUrlForRoute`, takes a string that specifies a route and appends it to a string specifying the location of a grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af626-131">Specifica una particolare regola di grammatica.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af626-131">This specifies a particular rule in that grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af626-132">Il metodo restituisce un `Uri` per la regola.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af626-132">The method returns a `Uri` for that rule.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="af626-133">Il secondo metodo, `CreateGrammarForRoute`, crea un' <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> elemento denominato `grammar` con un riferimento alla regola specificata dal `Uri` passato da `GrammarUrlForRoute`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af626-133">The second method, `CreateGrammarForRoute`, creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> element named `grammar` with a rule reference specified by the `Uri` passed to it by `GrammarUrlForRoute`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af626-134">Si noti che la variabile denominata _route è un membro di una classe contenitore.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af626-134">Note that the variable named _route is a member of an enclosing class.</span></span>  
  
```  
private Uri GrammarUrlForRoute(string route)  
{  
  return new Uri("http://localhost/MyBus/MyBusLocations.grxml#LocationsForRoute" + route);  
}  
  
private SrgsDocument CreateGrammarForRoute()  
{  
  SrgsDocument grammar = new SrgsDocument();  
  grammar.Mode = SrgsGrammarMode.Voice;  
  SrgsRule rule = new SrgsRule("LocationsForRoute" + _route);  
  SrgsRuleRef ruleref = new SrgsRuleRef(GrammarUrlForRoute(_route));  
  
  SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag tag = new SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag ("$.Location = $$");  
  
  rule.Elements.Add(ruleref);  
  rule.Elements.Add(tag);  
  grammar.Rules.Add(rule);  
  grammar.Root = rule;  
  return grammar;  
}  
```  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="af626-135">La variabile denominata _`route` viene dichiarato e definito nell'esempio precedente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af626-135">The variable named _`route` is undeclared and undefined in the preceding sample.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="af626-136">Deve essere dichiarato come un <xref:System.String> e contenere il numero di route per una route specifica bus prima che l'esempio precedente è compilata ed eseguita.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="af626-136">It should be declared as a <xref:System.String> and contain the route number for a particular bus route before the preceding sample is compiled and run.</span></span>

  
  
